trans-unit.source: Contains methods and properties that are used to manage queries to the tracking data that is contained in the SQL database used by a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService" />.
trans-unit.target: Contém propriedades e métodos que são usados para gerenciar consultas para os dados de acompanhamento que estão contidos no Banco de Dados SQL usado por um <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery> provides methods and properties that you can use in order to access certain kinds of tracking data stored in a SQL database by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery> fornece métodos e propriedades que você pode usar para acessar determinados tipos de dados armazenados em um banco de dados SQL do controle de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.

trans-unit.source: Access to this data is provided through <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects.
trans-unit.target: Acesso a dados é fornecido por meio de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objetos.

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A> to try to get a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> for a specific workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Você pode chamar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A> para tentar obter um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> para uma instância de fluxo de trabalho específico.

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A> to get a collection of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects that correspond workflow instances that have tracking data that matches a set of query parameters contained in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> that is passed as a parameter to the method.
trans-unit.target: Você pode chamar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A> para obter uma coleção de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objetos que correspondem a instâncias de fluxo de trabalho que possuem o controle que corresponde a um conjunto de dados de consulta parâmetros contidos em um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> que é passado como um parâmetro para o método.

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> class for more information about the kind of tracking data available and see the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> class for more information about the kind of queries that can be performed.
trans-unit.target: Consulte o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> de classe para obter mais informações sobre o tipo de dados disponíveis de controle e consulte o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> classe para obter mais informações sobre o tipo de consultas que podem ser executadas.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery" />.
